high_descs: Turn around and go near the fridge.
Take the cooking pan with egg from the refrigerator.
Turn around and go near the countertop.
Put the cooking pan with egg on the countertop and then put it into the microwave oven.
anns.task_desc: Placed the egg in the pan on the countertop and then put it in the microwave oven.

high_descs: Go ahead, when you reach the entrance, turn left. At the end of the fridge, turn right. Enter until you are in front of the shop window with doors. Turn right.
Open the cabinet door. Grab the pan with the egg. Close the cabinet door.
Place the pan with the egg on top of the countertop, to the right of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Find a frying pan with an egg. Place the pan and egg next to the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Turn right and left go to the pan in the fridge.
Pick up the egg from the countertop.
Put the pan on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Turn right and left go to in the fridge put Egg in the CounterTop
